Detailed Description

Temporary struct, used to build the tables m_imageByTileFeatureType and m_tileFeatureTypeByPOIType.

Implementation of constructor last in ServerTileMapFormatDesc to avoid long compilation times with MC2SimpleString and gcc-2.96
